com.googlecode.cqengine.entity

Class PrimaryKeyedMapEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.cqengine.entity.MapEntity
      • com.googlecode.cqengine.entity.PrimaryKeyedMapEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map

    public class PrimaryKeyedMapEntity
extends MapEntity
    An extension of MapEntity in which a particular entry in the map is designated as a primary key, and this primary key will then be used to compute hashCode and test for equality. This can avoid computing equality over all keys in the maps.
